{"tid":1630202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班撚樣為咗選舉 割夠席未？！","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:17:47.000Z","uid":45206,"like":34,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"01862419e519e3d014ce69259f5e92704ffaa04c","tid":1630202,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"打爛賣港鋪頭冇問題囉<br />\n<br />\n美心，黑社會嗰啲， 唔係言論自由嘅問題，係佢哋實質做咗好多嘢去害我哋呀嘛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以眼還眼，well-deserved，最多貼poster解釋點解要爆！其他藍店，我同意忍手嘅<br />\n<br />\n就快到11月選舉，連登吹風吹到痴曬線，不斷想人收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱蘋果日報仲出咗篇文，話示威者唔應該打爛舖頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報係泛民喉舌係人都知，你唔好話畀我聽過幾日泛民出嚟割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話你知，你一割，我寧願攬炒都唔投畀你！！！！！！"},{"pid":"4eddcaac6b4ae8845c8af845087e6bff1ce3f7ed","tid":1630202,"uid":201031,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武做野唔使需要班懦夫幫手<br />\n懦夫出街就害埋勇武手足<br />\n咪撚再叫和理非佢地係懦夫陀衰家<br />\n成事不足 敗事有餘</span></span>"},{"pid":"4717dbf8a5891c203176205abc2b09601f7bf056","tid":1630202,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eddcaac6b4ae8845c8af845087e6bff1ce3f7ed","tid":1630202,"uid":201031,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武做野唔使需要班懦夫幫手<br />\n懦夫出街就害埋勇武手足<br />\n咪撚再叫和理非佢地係懦夫陀衰家<br />\n成事不足 敗事有餘</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"唔好咁講，好多和理非做好多文宣"},{"pid":"45e27684a28ad24e234646659da5debf523283c8","tid":1630202,"uid":45206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:48:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"30de5da5a67fe8f7cbd8c5807ddf972ab760ef3a","tid":1630202,"uid":133235,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"選舉近了 左膠又出哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9deb9fcbdcf14a045ec6477f444f1906eec647","tid":1630202,"uid":45206,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30de5da5a67fe8f7cbd8c5807ddf972ab760ef3a","tid":1630202,"uid":133235,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"選舉近了 左膠又出哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:51:28.000Z","msg":"屌！！！私了個撞人的士佬都一班人衝出嚟擋住！！<br />\n<br />\n一到十一月選舉，啲人就發曬癲！！"},{"pid":"6fb2442c45bd54b10793eb17b1bf7342f7ac1a0d","tid":1630202,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:52:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7ebfec49bff7e4e218a61606a12b1f15b6cd315e","tid":1630202,"uid":130079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:52:50.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"0c34e8dad29ba3e361406b9fb189bedccb7d2e21","tid":1630202,"uid":221919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eddcaac6b4ae8845c8af845087e6bff1ce3f7ed","tid":1630202,"uid":201031,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武做野唔使需要班懦夫幫手<br />\n懦夫出街就害埋勇武手足<br />\n咪撚再叫和理非佢地係懦夫陀衰家<br />\n成事不足 敗事有餘</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:53:15.000Z","msg":"咪講得禁難聽 唔好完全否定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[求睇吓］請唔好孤立勇武 唔好重蹈覆轍！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628049</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"939c0e466397b29b4443023a445285c026bebb73","tid":1630202,"uid":52939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30de5da5a67fe8f7cbd8c5807ddf972ab760ef3a","tid":1630202,"uid":133235,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"選舉近了 左膠又出哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:53:27.000Z","msg":"打"},{"pid":"615eb4efc726b12e56da1577a8d427c7956b67d8","tid":1630202,"uid":53841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4eddcaac6b4ae8845c8af845087e6bff1ce3f7ed","tid":1630202,"uid":201031,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武做野唔使需要班懦夫幫手<br />\n懦夫出街就害埋勇武手足<br />\n咪撚再叫和理非佢地係懦夫陀衰家<br />\n成事不足 敗事有餘</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"你好似d和理非個個禮拜出街先講啦 你傻架"},{"pid":"9a5bc7acd2cd192f740789fad23b4d97d836c0b0","tid":1630202,"uid":64159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:54:46.000Z","msg":"裝修唔係問題但一定要噴原因，<br />\n同